text.tspan: The Government of China reported a cluster of cases of
pneumonia of unknown cause in Wuhan, Hubei Province.
WHO announces that the outbreak in Wuhan is
caused by a previously unknown type of coronavirus.
The virus was first identified in the Americas region - most
governments in the region acted quickly, adopting border
closures and implementing public health measures such as
movements and gatherings restrictions, quarantines, school
countries in Latin America and the Caribbean
